'''恙蟲病東方體'''（{{lang|la|''Orientia tsutsugamushi''}}）是[[恙蟲病|恙蟲病]]的病原體。其種小名「''tsutsugamushi''」源自於[[日语|日语]]「{{lang|ja|つつがむし}}」，為日本漢字「{{lang|ja|恙虫}}」和「病」兩字的發音<ref name="pmid14501995">{{cite journal|author=Watt G, Parola P|title=Scrub typhus and tropical rickettsioses|journal=Curr Opin Infect Dis|volume=16|issue=5|pages=429–36|date=October 2003|pmid=14501995|doi=10.1097/00001432-200310000-00009|url=http://meta.wkhealth.com/pt/pt-core/template-journal/lwwgateway/media/landingpage.htm?issn=0951-7375&volume=16&issue=5&spage=429|access-date=2016-04-29|archive-date=2012-03-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311154751/http://meta.wkhealth.com/pt/pt-core/template-journal/lwwgateway/media/landingpage.htm?issn=0951-7375&volume=16&issue=5&spage=429|dead-url=no}}</ref>。恙蟲東方體的自然病媒及傳染窩為[[鉤恙蟎屬|鉤恙蟎屬]]類的恙蟎<ref>{{cite journal|author=Traub R, Wisseman CL Jr|title=The ecology of chigger-borne rickettsiosis (scrub typhus)|journal=J Med Entomol|year=1974|volume=11|issue=3|pages=237–303|url=http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/esa/jme/1974/00000011/00000003/art00001|pmid=4212400|doi=10.1093/jmedent/11.3.237|access-date=2016-04-29|archive-date=2014-03-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302050300/http://www.ingentaconnect.com/content/esa/jme/1974/00000011/00000003/art00001|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Kelly2009">{{cite journal|author=Kelly DJ, Fuerst PA, Ching W-M, Richards AL|title=Scrub typhus: The geographic distribution of phenotypic and genotypic variants of ''Orientia tsutsugamushi''|journal=Clin Infect Dis|year=2009|volume=48|issue=s3|doi=10.1086/596576|pmid=19220144|pages=S203–30
}}</ref>。

恙蟲病東方體為胞內病原體，需寄生於真核細胞內才能繁殖。其外膜結構類似[[革兰氏阴性菌|革兰氏阴性菌]]，但並不容易以[[革蘭氏染色|革蘭氏染色]]染色，必須採用{{tsl|en|Gimenez stain}}。恙蟲病東方體具有多種血清型，主要血清型包含 Karp（占總感染病例的半數）<ref name="Kelly2009"/>，另外還有Gilliam（25%）<ref name="Kelly2009"/>、Kato（<10%）<ref name="Kelly2009"/>，以及Kawasaki等<ref>{{cite journal|vauthors=Yamamoto S, Kawabata N, Tamura A, etal|title=Immunological properties of ''Rickettsia tsutsugamushi,'' Kawasaki strain, isolated from a patient in Kyushu|journal=Microbiol Immunol|year=1986|volume=30|issue=7|doi=10.1111/j.1348-0421.1986.tb02988.x|pmid=3095612|url=http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1348-0421.1986.tb02988.x/abstract|pages=611–20|access-date=2016-04-29|archive-date=2017-09-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170921145741/http://onlinelibrary.wiley.com/doi/10.1111/j.1348-0421.1986.tb02988.x/abstract|dead-url=no}}</ref>。恙蟲東方體的血清型變化相當多樣<ref>{{cite journal
